# ─── User data + dev credentials (sensitive!) ──────────────────
# Contains:
#   - .dev_credentials.json  (Google OAuth client_id/secret — developer-side)
#   - config.json            (user-facing app settings + Plaid keys)
#   - tax_data.json          (parsed slips, access tokens, etc.)
#   - documents/             (uploaded PDFs)
# NEVER commit this folder.
data/

